  "prompt": "Is there any availability in Prestige Falcon City?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, I don't have real-time access to current availability for properties in Prestige Falcon City. To obtain the most accurate and up-to-date information, I recommend the following steps:\n\n1. **Contact Prestige Homes Directly:**\n   - **Website:** Visit the official [Prestige Homes website](https://www.prestigehomes.com.ng) for detailed information about Prestige Falcon City, including available units, floor plans, and pricing.\n   - **Customer Service:** Reach out to their customer service team via phone or email. Contact details are typically available on their website.\n   \n2. **Visit a Sales Office:**\n   - If you're located near Falcon City, Abuja, consider visiting a Prestige Homes sales office in person. This can provide you with immediate information and the opportunity to tour available properties.\n   \n3. **Check Online Real Estate Platforms:**\n   - Websites like [Jumia House](https://www.jumia.com.ng/house-for-sale/) (now part of Jumia Apartments) or [PropertyPro.ng](https://www.propertypro.ng/) often list available properties and can provide additional insights into availability and pricing.\n   \n4. **Consult a Local Real Estate Agent:**\n   - Engaging with a local real estate professional who specializes in Abuja properties can offer personalized assistance and up-to-date information on Prestige Falcon City and other developments.\n\n**About Prestige Falcon City:**\nPrestige Falcon City is a prominent real estate development located in Falcon City of Abuja, Nigeria. It is known for offering a range of residential units, including apartments, duplexes, and possibly other housing options, catering to various budget levels and preferences. The development typically features modern amenities, security, and convenient access to key areas within Abuja.\n\nFor the most accurate and specific information regarding availability, pricing, and booking procedures, contacting Prestige Homes directly is your best course of action.",
